> </label>\n</p>\n<p><label> Your message (optional)<br />\n<textarea cols=\"40\" rows=\"10\" maxlength=\"2000\" aria-invalid=\"false\" name=\"your-message\"></textarea> </label>\n</p>\n<noscript>\n		<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api/fallback?k=6LcibnArAAAAAHsx2RIbfLNVvL5k-x_ea9c1Vafy\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"310\" height=\"430\">\n		</iframe>\n		<textarea name=\"g-recaptcha-response\" rows=\"3\" cols=\"40\" placeholder=\"reCaptcha Response Here\">\n		</textarea>\n</noscript>\n<p><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" />\n</p><p style=\"display: none !important;\" data-prefix=\"_wpcf7_ak_\"><label>&#916;<textarea name=\"_wpcf7_ak_hp_textarea\" cols=\"45\" rows=\"8\" maxlength=\"100\"></textarea></label><input type=\"hidden\" id=\"ak_js_3\" name=\"_wpcf7_ak_js\" value=\"83\"/></p>\n</form>\n		</aside>\n		<style>.hw-el-76677d1{--hw-form-fn-wt:500;}</style>','','https://antiviruspoint.org/shop/contact-us/','','<img src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/themes/filson/images/default-thumbnail.jpg\" width=\"640px\" height=\"384px\" class=\"image-size-name\" />',0.0000,0.0000,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'page',300553,'','','','en_US',0,'','',0.00);
INSERT INTO `fqsi_yith_wcas_data_index_lookup` (`post_id`, `name`, `description`, `summary`, `url`, `sku`, `thumbnail`, `min_price`, `max_price`, `onsale`, `instock`, `stock_quantity`, `is_purchasable`, `rating_count`, `average_rating`, `total_sales`, `post_type`, `post_parent`, `product_type`, `parent_category`, `tags`, `lang`, `featured`, `custom_fields`, `custom_taxonomies`, `boost`) VALUES (91228,'About Us','<img width=\"10\" height=\"7\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_1.webp\" alt=\"\" />                                                               <h2>About Antiviruspoint - Your Go-to Security Partner</h2>     Antiviruspoint is dedicated to your online security and protecting people rather than just devices. Our solutions are designed to adapt to the unique needs of our customers, enabling them to navigate the online world with confidence through seamless, user-friendly protection. We offer you the confidence to surf online without the need to look for online thefts and enjoy your browsing experience.\n\nWe can effectively provide Protection from Malware, Data Security, Safe Browsing, Prevention of System Slowdown, Automatic Updates, and most importantly your peace of mind.\n\n<pre><code>     &lt;figure&gt;&lt;img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_3.png\" alt=\"\" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Online Support 24/7&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We offer round-the-clock customer support to assist with any security concerns or issues you may encounter.&lt;/p&gt;                 &lt;figure&gt;&lt;img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_4.png\" alt=\"\" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Privacy Protection&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We offer features such as secure browsing, and identity monitoring to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, allowing you to maintain control over your online privacy.&lt;/p&gt;                 &lt;figure&gt;&lt;img width=\"100\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_2.png\" alt=\"\" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cloud-Based Security&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We leverage cloud-based technology to boost performance and minimize the strain on system resources, providing quick and efficient protection without compromising your device\'s speed.&lt;/p&gt;                    &lt;figure&gt;&lt;img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_6.webp\" alt=\"\" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What do we do?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;We offer advanced antivirus and security software designed to protect devices, data, and online activities from a wide range of cyber threats. Our solutions include real-time malware detection, identity protection, secure browsing, and privacy tools to ensure that our customers can navigate the digital world safely. \n</code></pre>\n\n</p>                    <figure><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_5.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Our Mission</h3><p>Our mission is to deliver strong, dependable, and easy-to-use cybersecurity solutions that safeguard individuals and businesses from ever-changing online threats. </p>                 <figure><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/about_image_7.webp\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>History Of Us</h3><p>Antiviruspoint is founded with the goal of creating a safer digital environment. We have led the way in cybersecurity for years, offering innovative solutions that protect both individuals and businesses from online threats. </p>                 <h2>AntivirusPoint.org â Trusted Digital Antivirus Reseller</h2><br />\n         <aside   >\n            <h4 class=\'hw-title-box\'><br />\n                                    At AntivirusPoint.org, operated by Infinity Solutions, we specialize in selling genuine antivirus license keys and digital software products. Our mission is to make cybersecurity accessible and affordable to individuals and businesses worldwide.  We partner with authorized distributors to provide instant delivery of license keys for popular antivirus brands. All products sold are digital, delivered directly via email, ensuring fast and secure service.  Our team is committed to transparency, customer support, and compliance with local and international regulations.  Business Name: Infinity Solutions Website: AntivirusPoint.org Email Support: Infinity@antiviruspoint.org Phone Support:+1-855-574-5124\n        </h4><br />\n            {\"title\":\"All\",\"title_box_all\":\"All\",\"number\":\"5\",\"ignore_sticky_posts\":\"yes\",\"excerpt\":\"yes\",\"meta\":{\"meta_category\":\"yes\",\"meta_date\":\"yes\"},\"layout\":\"list\",\"list_layout\":\"list_1\",\"post_type\":\"post\",\"action\":\"hexwp_post_list\",\"post_status\":\"publish\"}\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/category/uncategorized/\">Uncategorized</a></li><li>August 27, 2025</li><br />\n    </ul> \n    <h3><a href=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/?p=90008184\"></a></h3>\n            What was the last thing you searched for online? Why were you looking for it?\n        </aside>','','https://antiviruspoint.org/shop/about-us/','','<img src=\"https://antiviruspoint.org/wp-content/themes/filson/images/default-thumbnail.jpg\" width=\"640px\" height=\"384px\" class=\"image-size-name\" />',0.0000,0.0000,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'page',300553,'','','','en_US',0,'','',0.00);
